Package server.model

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    JDBCredentials
    Interface that stores info needed to connect to the tooshopitem database.
    PasswordDecoder
    Password Decoder is an interface that is meant to decode a password and check if it is the same and the true password.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CaesarCypher
    class that implements PasswordDecoder and decodes CaesarCypher with a right shift of 1.
    DatabaseConnector
    DatabaseConnector connects to a database and asks/receives information from that database.
    DecreaseItemQuantityInDatabase
    class that extends Database Connector to provide decreasing quantity of an item in database functionality, as well as checking if there's a need to create a new order.
    FindItemInDatabase
    class that extends Database Connector to provide getting an item based on id in database functionality.
    GetAllItemsInDatabase
    class that extends Database Connector to provide getting all items in database functionality.
    GetAllOrdersFromDatabase  
    InsertItem
    class that extends Database Connector to provide inserting an item in database functionality.
    InsertSupplier
    class that extends Database Connector to provide inserting a supplier in database functionality.
    LoginValidator
    class that extends Database Connector to login/credential checking in database functionality.
    SearchDatabase
    class that extends Database Connector to provide searchng for multiple items in database functionality.
